     <br/>
     – options for additional rear and side lights (compatible with various light packs)
     <br/>
     – Painted, plastic and chrome variants for side tubes, painted variants with own template
     <br/>
     – Custom license plate option
     <br/>
     – Slots for signs/stickers, including French ‘Angles morts’
    </p>
